{"tid":2230911,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"違反隔離令求返美照顧病母 持美籍香港女子遭還柙 杜浩成:如果有市民唔好彩受感染 病情可能比妳母親嚴重","createTime":"2020-10-05T09:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T09:57:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a35cff654bc192da259944b425e9314fd5ee2e43","tid":2230911,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:18:06.000Z","msg":"早年移民美國的香港女子早前因事回港，惟在未完成14天隔離的情況下便離開檢疫住處，並前赴機場打算返美，結果遭截獲，被控未獲授權離開檢疫地點罪。案件今日提堂，女被告辯稱因得悉在美母親病重，才會犯案，又出示證明母女關係的文件，要求裁判官杜浩成批准她先行離港，以便返美照顧母親。惟杜官指：「攞份文件就走，如果有市民唔好彩受感染，病情可能比妳母親嚴重。」杜官最終下令被告還柙候訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201005/KK7MIJ7NWFCCLMYB2PQJSFUBFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201005%2FKK7MIJ7NWFCCLMYB2PQJSFUBFQ%2F&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGI5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=fe28f1d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201005%2FKK7MIJ7NWFCCLMYB2PQJSFUBFQ%2F&h=11dcbb30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201005/KK7MIJ7NWFCCLMYB2PQJSFUBFQ/</a>"},{"pid":"a3ae4ac7124621198f146c9db0c0e11c40422298","tid":2230911,"uid":107577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:19:02.000Z","msg":"呢單嘢真係唔講得笑"},{"pid":"cb0889d6cf99d27a28a7a8733c6438bfbd0b4ce1","tid":2230911,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:21:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c9ee68d111532a5867633aaba5ffa62da92ac01","tid":2230911,"uid":38518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:22:04.000Z","msg":"下次就唔只用喺隔離人士身上"},{"pid":"b2f4a79f766733123cf7a60d9d745ac468b68485","tid":2230911,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:23:49.000Z","msg":"痴鳩線 咁都要還押<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa15996d2a9faae6591254a19fe49c6a60f2871","tid":2230911,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislik